{"tid":1740930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英領事館職員Simon Cheng被中國秘密警察毒打虐待","createTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:17:54.000Z","uid":167289,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"26663993024d0f9756aa2dea1f070591f0622773","tid":1740930,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"Former U.K. Consulate Employee Says Chinese Secret Police Tortured Him<br />\n<br />\nSimon Cheng, a former employee of Britain&rsquo;s Hong Kong consulate, claimed Chinese secret police beat him, deprived him of sleep and chained him spread-eagled as they pressed him for information about the pro-democracy protests that have swept the city since June.<br />\n<br />\nHe told The Wall Street Journal that he was questioned repeatedly about the role his interrogators presumed Britain was playing in fomenting the unrest.<br />\n<br />\nU.K. Foreign Secretary Dominic Raab said China&rsquo;s treatment of Mr. Cheng &ldquo;amounts to torture.&rdquo; China&rsquo;s Foreign Ministry didn&rsquo;t respond to a request for comment, nor did the police in Shenzhen, where he was detained.<br />\n<br />\nSee More Coverage &rsaquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/former-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602?mod=djemalertNEWS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fformer-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602%3Fmod%3DdjemalertNEWS&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=986f5ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/former-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602?mod=djemalertNEWS</a>"},{"pid":"86e81eeee27ecf382c15b01ddaaed08b28f5b76e","tid":1740930,"uid":184581,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"中國警察=香港警察"},{"pid":"5beb0eebfe43128af1cd184edf595d2fa31b0cd4","